CHAVEZ; Photo, Above, students at San Fernando High School watch from a 
second-floor classroom as fellow students participate in protest. Below, 
hallway at the high school is empty during the protest. TORU KAWANA / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
