<HEADLINE>
<P>
TODAY'S QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"He didn't accept the call as being a valid call. He didn't do anything." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Sheriff Sherman Block, on an incident in which a frantic 911 caller 
reporting a gang shooting and fearing for his life was told, "Have a nice day," 
by a deputy, who hung up on him. 
</P>
