<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Frank's: A Veritable Tread Mill Even after just a quick, rubbernecking 
glance at Frank's place, one has no trouble figuring out he runs an orderly and 
well-rounded business. Above right, a would-be vendor offers a single tire for 
sale, but the deal went flat. At right, three pedestrians tread lightly past 
the signs that make it plain what Frank's Tires, at University Avenue and 42nd 
Street, is all about. DAVID McNEW 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
