<DOCNO> LA012889-0080 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 11194 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 28, 1989, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part 3; Page 1; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
