<P>
FHP International Corp., a Fountain Valley-based health maintenance 
organization, reported net income of $4.9 million in its second fiscal quarter 
ended Dec. 31, up 33% from $3.7 million for the same period of fiscal 1988. The 
company posted revenue in the second fiscal quarter of $160.9 million, up 39% 
from $116 million for the second quarter a year ago. Net income for the first 
two quarters of fiscal 1989 was $9 million, up 45% from $6.2 million for the 
